Package crimeSpy.crimeData

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DAL_able
    DATA ACCESS LAYER Interface
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CrimeCollection
    A collection of CrimeRecords.
    CrimeCollectionManager
    Manages collections of crimes (CrimeCollection object) Will provide search and filter functionality.
    CrimeLocation
    The CrimeLocation class is intended to be used for location data storage and methods for the CrimeRecord.
    CrimeRecord
    Define the crime record object.
    CrimeType
    CrimeType object abstracts information about a crime (it's type)
    CSVFileHandler
    A class to manage interactions between the crimeSpy system and the various filetypes.
    FilterCrimeCollection
    filters a crimeCollection based on filter crime information specified by the user and produces and filterOptions (not implement yet) to produce a filtered CrimeCollection
    OR_Map
    Provides a 1:1 mapping of a CrimeRecord object into a structure that can be passes into the DAL (data access layer) for easy writing and vice versa.
    SearchCrimeCollection
    Created by Zachary Todd on 24/08/2015.
    SQLiteDBHandler
    A class to manage interactions between the crimeSpy system and the SQLite Database.
